paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as (
select distinct pogId, 
                categoryGroup, 
                count(distinct subOrderId) as sold,
                ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY count(distinct subOrderId) DESC) AS rn 
from `all(agCmDump)` 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),to_date(from_unixtime((orderDate)/1000))) between 13 and 46 
group by pogId,categoryGroup
)
select distinct pogId, 
                categoryGroup, 
                sold 
from cte 
",1000)

paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select distinct b.pogId, 
                b.categoryGroup, 
                case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then 'FB'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%direct%' then 'Direct'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%re-targeting%' then 'RTC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%notification%' then 'Notification'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%newsletter%' then 'Newsletter'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%unattributedutm%' then 'Unattributed'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%other%' then 'OMC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%google%' then 'Google'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%whatsapp%' then 'WA'
                     end as Channels,
                count(distinct a.subOrderId)
                
from `temp.atb` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate) between 13 and 46 
group by pogId,categoryGroup, case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then 'FB'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%direct%' then 'Direct'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%re-targeting%' then 'RTC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%notification%' then 'Notification'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%newsletter%' then 'Newsletter'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%unattributedutm%' then 'Unattributed'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%other%' then 'OMC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%google%' then 'Google'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%whatsapp%' then 'WA'
                     end
",1000)

paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select distinct b.pogId, 
                b.categoryGroup, 
                case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then 'FB'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%direct%' then 'Direct'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%re-targeting%' then 'RTC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%notification%' then 'Notification'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%newsletter%' then 'Newsletter'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%unattributedutm%' then 'Unattributed'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%other%' then 'OMC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%google%' then 'Google'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%whatsapp%' then 'WA'
                     end as Channels,
                count(distinct a.subOrderId) as sold
from `temp.atb` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate) between 13 and 43 
group by pogId,categoryGroup, case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then 'FB'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%direct%' then 'Direct'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%re-targeting%' then 'RTC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%notification%' then 'Notification'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%newsletter%' then 'Newsletter'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%unattributedutm%' then 'Unattributed'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%other%' then 'OMC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%google%' then 'Google'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%whatsapp%' then 'WA'
                     end
",1000)

paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select distinct b.pogId, 
                case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then 'FB'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%direct%' then 'Direct'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%re-targeting%' then 'RTC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%notification%' then 'Notification'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%newsletter%' then 'Newsletter'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%unattributedutm%' then 'Unattributed'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%other%' then 'OMC'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%google%' then 'Google'
                     when lower(a.Channel) like '%whatsapp%' then 'WA'
                     end as Channels,
                count(distinct a.subOrderId) as sold
from `temp.atb` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate) between 13 and 43 
group by pogId, Channels
",1000)

run(sql="
select distinct b.categoryGroup,
                b.pogId, 
                count(distinct case when lower(a.utmSource) like '%criteo%' then a.subOrderId end) as criteo,
                count(distinct case when lower(a.utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' then a.subOrderId end) as rtbhouse,
                count(distinct case when lower(a.utmSource) like '%adinterest_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%admitad_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_appdrawer_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_siteplug_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_tiles_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affnetmedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affyguru_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%cashkaro%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%earnkaro%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%coupondunia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%cuelinks_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%globalemedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%gopaisa_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%grabon_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%icubes_846_3162_%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%inrdeals_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%mediaxpedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%mobavenue_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%optimisemedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%paisawapas_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%spiffy_c2c_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%valueleaf_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%whizadsbay_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%xapads_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%xare_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%desidime_846%' then a.subOrderId end) as affiliate
from `temp.atb` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate) between 13 and 43 
group by categoryGroup, pogId
",1000)

select distinct b.categoryGroup,
                b.pogId,

                count(distinct case when lower(a.utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' then a.subOrderId end) as rtbhouse,
                count(distinct case when lower(a.utmSource) like '%adinterest_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%admitad_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_appdrawer_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_siteplug_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affinityveve_tiles_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affnetmedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%affyguru_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%cashkaro%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%earnkaro%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%coupondunia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%cuelinks_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%globalemedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%gopaisa_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%grabon_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%icubes_846_3162_%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%inrdeals_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%mediaxpedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%mobavenue_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%optimisemedia_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%paisawapas_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%spiffy_c2c_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%valueleaf_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%whizadsbay_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%xapads_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%xare_846%' or lower(a.utmSource) like '%desidime_846%' then a.subOrderId end) as affiliate,
                sum(c.NMIncAd) as nm
from `temp.atb` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
left join `last45Days(unitEconomicsBaseTable)` c on a.subOrderId=c.subOrderId 
where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate) between 13 and 43 
group by categoryGroup, pogId
",1000)
